    %% Bindings
    SA_Argo -->|bound via| CRB_Argo
    CRB_Argo -->|grants| CR_Argo

    SA_Server -->|bound via| CRB_Server
    CRB_Server -->|grants| CR_Server

    %% argo-cluster-role permissions
    CR_Argo -->|manages| Pods
    CR_Argo -->|reads| ConfigMaps
    CR_Argo -->|manages| PVCs
    CR_Argo -->|reads| ServiceAccounts
    CR_Argo -->|creates| Events
    CR_Argo -->|reads| Secrets
    CR_Argo -->|manages| PDBs
    CR_Argo -->|manages| Workflows
    CR_Argo -->|manages| TaskSets
    CR_Argo -->|manages| ArtifactGC
    CR_Argo -->|reads| Templates
    CR_Argo -->|watches| TaskResults
    CR_Argo -->|manages| CronWFs

    %% argo-server-cluster-role permissions
    CR_Server -->|reads/deletes| ServerPods
    CR_Server -->|reads/creates| ServerSecrets
    CR_Server -->|reads| ServerConfigMaps
    CR_Server -->|creates| ServerEvents
    CR_Server -->|reads| ServerSA
    CR_Server -->|full CRUD| ServerCRDs

    %% Aggregate roles
    CR_View -.->|"aggregates to<br/>view role"| Templates
    CR_Edit -.->|"aggregates to<br/>edit role"| Workflows
    CR_Admin -.->|"aggregates to<br/>admin role"| TaskSets

